data.description: Welcome to your new, wonderfully designed RANCH+LOFT style home backing to OPEN SPACE! With quick access to I-25 and Centerra Shopping center, this sought-after home is a rare find. Enjoy all the conveniences of main floor living with the added space and flexibility of a second story loft!  Constructed in 2017, why buy new with the added expense of window coverings and landscaping when this home already has it all? Upon entry,  a spacious foyer welcomes you along with the first of 3 bedrooms, a full bath, and large main floor laundry room. Further along the way, the open kitchen overlooks the family room and offers views of the back yard. The kitchen has a granite island and countertops, stainless steel appliances and includes a gas stove. The main floor primary suite is separated from the other bedrooms for a quiet retreat. Melt into your bathroom with a large walk-in shower and custom built walk-in closet. Need more space? The second-floor flex space offers so many options; such as an office area, workout space or a second family room. The en-suite is perfect for additional privacy. The backyard is sprinkled and tastefully landscaped. Your new home is set in a quiet neighborhood with immediate access to miles of walking trails, disc golf course, and parks. This is the one you've been waiting for!
